name: Hunter69 v1
description:
Hunter69 v1

release date: 17 January 2023

Due to many DM requests on Discord, I decided to share version 1 of my model which is a merge of some popular models (forgot which ones) and 3 private ones (not from Civitai or any other public website - but with permission), which I have perfectionized into the ideal checkpoint/model for creating stunning real life looking female nude models.

Despite the possibility of being able to create cartoons/anime/drawings/males/objects, I have focussed a lot towards generating female (solo) nude art models similar to the style of that from MetArt & Domai.

I'm currently am working on v3, which is already a huge improvement over v1 after v2 became corrupted (in the sense of missing a few amount of bytes during transfer from server to server) and therefore being unable to load it.

When will v3 be released?
Most-likely around April 2022 or earlier, as I want to merge it with more embeddings as well as merge it with a yet to be privately released model trained completely by myself.
There won't be new versions of this particular model on Civitai, Hunter v3 will most-likely be released with a different name and of course on Civitai!

Updates
If you like to stay up to date by seeing many images that I've made using (for now using codename) Hunter69 v3, then please follow me on Patreon where I will also share some of the prompts I have used which are not that far of from v1.

Merges
I support creativity, if you plan to use this model for merges, you do not have to credit me, that's up to you. But thanks in advance for doing so.

Support my efforts
Want to support my efforts, which take a lot of time, testing, plotting, comparing, rendering, you can subscribe to my Patreon for as many months as you like or simply buy me a coffee and help me reach my goal.

You will not only help support me with a brand new videocard I'm saving for, which will make training of my new future models from scratch (no merging) much faster, but you'll also get access to HQ (1024/1280/1368px) images I have created myself and more!

Notes

  • This model requires vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

  • Despite me using my model mostly for 21-30 year old Asians females, it does work for any ethnicity and/or age as shown in the gallery of X/Y plotting

  • Not enough Examples? Visit my site here (be aware that all images shown are based on Hunter69 v1, and I have stopped updating, new v3 images will be on my Patreon)
